				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Only based on what I went through 4 years ago.
<br />

<br />
#1, delete him and create something more fun than a stinkin' high elf. :p
<br />

<br />
#2, don't bother buying all the low level pets.  Water is probably a good all-purpose low level pet (I went with air, which was a good choice back when pets drew aggro when at rest).
<br />

<br />
As a druid you know that you can't nuke & sit.  Keep in mind that critters consider /pet attack as a nuke.  You have to wait a few seconds before sitting.
<br />

<br />
Hmm, for soloing perhaps it would be a good idea to buy earth too, for the roots.<br />_________________<br />Binnen Minder
<br />
Gnome God At-Large (so to speak)
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=977280" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=977280</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
