				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Only tip I can offer if you are new to pet classes is look for mages (and necro's and beastlords) and watch how they solo.  It's generally a good exercise in patience to solo effectively.  Also pay close attention to mages and how differently they play when in groups.
<br />

<br />
That's about it.
<br />

<br />
Oh!  
<br />

<br />
One more thing...
<br />

<br />
WhatEVER you do, if you DO re-create...for heaven's sake don't (repeat: DON'T) create a gnome!  OMG do they STINK!  I mean man!  They don't even make good cup holders...mugs of ale keep slippin off their bald little heads and yer always trippin over the little varmits.  Ever seen one eat?  *shudder*...it's like watching an amoeba reach out with spindly little arms and...oh...I just can't continue...the vision is just too gruesome.
