				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Earth pets are the best to solo with, they have the most hp and they root at 13 second intervals in case you nuke one too many times, air pets are nice for the stun when in group, and water pets hit the hardest and Backstab at higher levels, fire has a ds, but not many hp. I solo'd a lot in Stonebrunt when i was a wee mage, and at one point i was getting about a level every 3 to 4 hours, if you need anymore info, or if you want me to show you the best spot in SB to solo (yes theres is a best spot) send me a tell or reply here, and ill be happy to help ya out. Oh, also go to Najena and do the focus quest as soon as you are able to go in safely they help on pets up to 49 or 51 i think.<br />_________________<br />Sticx 64 Arch Mage
<br />
243 Tinkerer, 188 Researcher
<br />
 
<br />
Kaeolan 55 Preserver</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
