				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I don't think it makes that much difference, but I DO think that it helps somewhat.  What I do with my baby necro is keep on the lookout for critters with weapons.  The weapons suck but they're likely better than the summoned dagger.  Shields as well can't hurt!
<br />

<br />
Zambik likes to give pet gifts away but summoning that stuff can be really annoying if you don't know the person, so although those weapons would be seriously nice (level 61-63 weapons) I wouldn't ask a stranger for them (I know you wouldn't) but DO feel free to ask a guildy. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />  The muzzle (haste) and belt (hp & stat boosts) are also nice.  I think that Zargot even has one more thing to give away so hit him up for stuff! hehe<br />_________________<br />Binnen Minder
